"called the Sidebar. You can use the Sidebar to navigate to different parts "
"of the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"On the left-hand side of the dashboard and throughout the ClimWeb is a menu "
"called the Sidebar. You can use the Sidebar to navigate to different parts "
