msgstr ""
"Password to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. This "
"setting is used in conjunction with `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` when "
"authenticating to the SMTP server. If either of these settings is empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."

